{{Use DMY dates|date=September 2017}} The '''Sumathi Best Teledrama Script Award''' is presented annually in Sri Lanka by the Sumathi Group of Campany associated with many commercial brands for the best Sri Lankan script of the year in television screen.<ref>{{cite web|title=About Sumathi Awards|url=http://sumathiawards.lk/about-sumathi-awards.php|website=www.sumathiawards.lk}}</ref>
The award was first given in 1995. Following is a list of the winners of this prestigious title since then.<ref>{{cite web|title=Sumathi Award winners in each year|url=http://sumathiawards.lk/sumathi-awards-winners.php|website=www.sumathiawards.lk}}</ref>
